title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1994-10-15
lineage: DAT > Sony PCM-R500 > Tascam DA-3000> WAV 16/48. Recorded and transferred by Jim Wise. edited and mastered SIRMick.
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Little Red Rooster, Stagger Lee, Black Throated Wind*, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, Candyman , Easy Ansers, Deal

Set 2

Here Comes Sunshine, Victim Or The Crime, Way to Go Home, New Speedway Boogie, Drums-> Space-> The Last Time, Standing On the Moon, One More Saturday Night, E: I Want to Tell You

* Weir on acoustic guitar
